<DocsLayout title="Installation - Material Charts">
  <h1>Installation</h1>
  
  <p>Add <a href="https://pub.dev/packages/material_charts" >Material Charts </a>to your Flutter project by adding the following to your <code>pubspec.yaml</code>:</p>

  <pre><code>dependencies:
  material_charts: latest_version</code></pre>

  <h2>Basic Usage</h2>

  <p>Here's a simple example of how to create a bar chart:</p>

  <pre><code>import 'package:flutter/material.dart';
import 'package:material_charts/material_charts.dart';

MaterialBarChart(
  data: [
    BarChartData(value: 30, label: 'A'),
    BarChartData(value: 70, label: 'B'),
    BarChartData(value: 50, label: 'C'),
  ],
  style: BarChartStyle(
    gridColor: Colors.grey.shade300,
    backgroundColor: Colors.white,
  ),
  showGrid: true,
  showValues: true,
);</code></pre>

